Source: The Lychee-Lily raganade is a dish originating from the country of Dysatria. It is prepared as a course named Parchrisvin and has a variation called Glutinto. The people of Dysatria are called Landersons and their currency is called Wupam. The main ingredient of the Lychee-Lily raganade is Fraidsuds.
Translation: 라이치-릴리 라가나드는 디스아트리아라는 나라에서 유래된 요리입니다. Parchrisvin이라는 코스의 요리로 준비되며 Glutinto라는 변형이 있습니다. 디스아트리아 사람들은 랜더슨이라고 불리며 그들의 통화는 Wupam이라고 불립니다. 라이치-릴리 라가나드의 주 재료는 Fraidsuds입니다.

Source: The Boomblasters Bowl is located in Lapata and serves as the ground for MidgenstUnited. MidgenstUnited is a team in the RimorchDivision, which is a league in the country of Relyida. The season for MidgenstUnited in the ChromoniaDerby was during the year 2082-83.
